{
  "stem": "26359.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was there with a medic, Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was in charge of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This wasn't so good for me, because again, I was in touch with the Ukrainian boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they tried to question my identification, my ID.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind-- cleaning work, taking care of sick people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were many sick people used to came to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't give them too much medications.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the person is sick, it's not worth it to live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They can't do nothing with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many people died prematurely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was people with VD, syphilis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was people, some of them were-- one person was-- I remember he was jumping on the table.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He must have been very bad temperature, 103, something, very high temperature, and he was jumping.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- the people there, I remember, they didn't get too much medication.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if the person is sick, they let them finish up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They let them die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't-- and I of course, I had to help these people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had to bring the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The food we brought from the main office, from the main hospital, to the [NON-ENGLISH] barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was going on also for quite a few-- for a long time, till 1943, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they didn't really provide medical care, because these were the guest arbeiters, the gastarbeiters from the east?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You want to talk about the soldiers?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, the soldiers was the regular care, regular hospitals with linen, white linen, change the linen every day, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had very good care, the soldiers who came from the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first place, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first place wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they taught me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
